with a little stimmy.

136
00:05:30,293 --> 00:05:32,503
Lil' stimmy.

137
00:05:32,545 --> 00:05:33,629
Are you trying to do this?

138
00:05:33,671 --> 00:05:35,215
Yes!

139
00:05:35,257 --> 00:05:37,259
And I want stimmy
to get a hook that'll do that.

140
00:05:37,300 --> 00:05:39,052
<i>When no such hook</i>
<i>was available,</i>

141
00:05:39,094 --> 00:05:42,764
<i>Lucille found other means</i>
<i>to mollify her alibi--</i>

142
00:05:42,805 --> 00:05:45,225
<i>both of which were unveiled</i>
<i>at a family meeting.</i>

143
00:05:45,267 --> 00:05:48,353
