I was the key witness.

145
00:05:50,105 --> 00:05:51,689
- You're the star witness.
- Oh.

146
00:05:51,731 --> 00:05:54,567
Because it was your life
I was going after to save.

147
00:05:54,609 --> 00:05:56,069
He fell off the boat.

148
00:05:56,111 --> 00:05:58,071
- He'll tell you in my own words.
- (groans)

149
00:05:58,113 --> 00:05:59,572
(mumbles):
Homosexuals kidnapped...

150
00:05:59,614 --> 00:06:02,033
